Shark -- Hive on Spark

Building
Shark requires Scala 2.9.1

It is built with Simple Build Tool (SBT), which we have included.
To build Shark run:
sbt/sbt compile

Shark runs with Hive-0.7.0 and uses the Hive configurations specified in $HIVE_HOME/conf
$HIVE_HOME must be set before running Shark

For information on setting up Hive or HiveQl, please read:
https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/Hive/GettingStarted

Shark also uses the Spark configurations specified in $SPARK_HOME/conf/spark-env.sh

For information on Spark, please read:
https://github.com/mesos/spark